49:23.717 --> 49:25.886
Hey, Bill Rudolph,
thank you for calling me back.

49:25.970 --> 49:28.097
It's James Douglas Clayton.

49:28.180 --> 49:32.350
We met at M.I.T. in Boston
at -- we -- Sp@rtacus --

49:32.433 --> 49:34.352
Sp@rtacus --

49:34.435 --> 49:38.106
and I was
with my family for a while,

49:38.147 --> 49:42.359
but now I'm back, and I'm ready
to raise the bar with Sp@rtacus,

49:42.442 --> 49:44.570
'cause we can raise the bar
with Sp@rtacus

49:44.653 --> 49:46.113
and change things.

49:46.196 --> 49:47.947
Will you call me...

50:10.427 --> 50:11.595
Nice hit.

50:11.636 --> 50:12.971
What the --

50:13.054 --> 50:14.931
You mind?

50:14.973 --> 50:17.016
My throat.

50:17.099 --> 50:19.894
Let go. Now.

50:19.977 --> 50:21.312
Now.

50:26.107 --> 50:27.650
What --

50:33.489 --> 50:35.866
I see you're living good.

50:38.076 --> 50:41.079
Get some clothes on.
We'll take a drive.

50:41.163 --> 50:42.164
A drive?

50:42.247 --> 50:44.498
Yeah. I'll wait outside.

50:53.758 --> 50:56.218
That booze is coming out
of your bones.

50:56.302 --> 50:58.596
What am I doing here?

50:58.679 --> 51:00.890
