I'm out.

51:00.973 --> 51:03.016
I don't have to play
your stupid games.

51:03.099 --> 51:05.352
Oh, but you will, James.

51:05.393 --> 51:09.397
You will play because
your particular engine --

51:09.481 --> 51:14.151
what drives you, moves you,
motivates you --

51:14.235 --> 51:15.736
