51:17.071 --> 51:19.114
Me.

51:19.198 --> 51:21.366
-All right, pull over.

51:21.449 --> 51:23.159
Pull over the goddamn car!

51:23.243 --> 51:26.287
-All right! Go ahead, get out.

51:26.371 --> 51:29.539
You lasted longer
on your interrogation exercise

51:29.581 --> 51:32.251
than any CT has
in the last 15 years.

51:32.334 --> 51:33.418
I broke!

51:33.502 --> 51:35.754
Everybody breaks!
That's the point!

51:35.796 --> 51:38.340
Damn thing doesn't stop
till you break.

51:38.423 --> 51:39.508
