Hey, Joey. Cappuccino.

01:02:09.876 --> 01:02:10.877
Sure.

01:02:15.589 --> 01:02:16.590
James.

01:02:16.632 --> 01:02:17.591
Hi.

01:02:17.633 --> 01:02:18.842
Hey. Hey.

01:02:18.926 --> 01:02:21.385
